<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=297&amp;p=2185#p2185"><![CDATA[
<strong>Add a Button to the Windows Backup And Restore Control Panel</strong>, so after you click this button, all you need to do is click &quot;Back-up&quot;<br /><ul><li>Command:<ul><li>%windir%\explorer.exe shell:::{B98A2BEA-7D42-4558-8BD1-832F41BAC6FD}</li></ul></li><li>Label:<ul><li>Back-Up</li></ul></li><li>Icon:<ul><li>sdcpl.dll </li><li>1</li></ul></li></ul><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=359">Tenzen</a> — Fri Mar 22, 2013 9:19 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
